OL,6,FA children's heart surgery service is
OL,7,Fin a "precarious" state amid concerns
OL,8,Fabout above-average death rates, a
OL,9,Freport has found.
OL,11,FHospital bosses have been told urgent
OL,12,Faction is needed to address a staffing
OL,13,Fcrisis in the Leeds congenital cardiac
OL,14,Fservice.
OL,16,FLeeds Teaching Hospitals NHS Trust
OL,17,Fordered an external review after
OL,18,Fconcerns were first raised by medics
OL,19,Fin November 2023.
