OL,6,FA report to the trust's next board
OL,7,Fmeeting said paediatric mortality
OL,8,Frates were within the expected range
OL,9,Fbetween 2021-2023.
OL,11,FBut outcomes after April 2023 showed
OL,12,F"a worrying and significant
OL,13,Fdeterioration, with risk-adjusted
OL,14,Fmortality rate running around three
OL,15,Ftimes the national average".
OL,17,F"During the same period, the rate of
OL,18,Fsignificant complications has
OL,19,Fincreased, including need for re-
OL,20,Foperations and very protracted length
OL,21,Fof stay," the report said.
