OL,6,FOne surgeon was due to retire and
OL,7,Fanother had decided not to return from
OL,8,Fa sabbatical, it said.
OL,10,FThere were "personality clashes" among
OL,11,Fstaff in the unit at Leeds General
OL,12,FInfirmary.
OL,14,FThe report said: "Some staff stated
OL,15,Fthat they no longer escalated concerns
OL,16,Fabout poor behaviour as there was
OL,17,Fsense that nothing would be done.
OL,19,F"Other staff cited examples of
OL,20,Fexcellent team working and
OL,21,Fprofessionalism."
