OL,6,FThe report praised the service for
OL,7,Fdealing with rising numbers of complex
OL,8,Fcases.
OL,10,FIt said: "However, some recent poor
OL,11,Fpatient outcomes and the imminent
OL,12,Fretirement of its senior surgeon now
OL,13,Fplaces the entire programme in a very
OL,14,Fprecarious state."
OL,16,FIt warned of national consequences and
OL,17,Fdirect impacts on services in
OL,18,FLiverpool and Newcastle.
OL,26,@rD@JOUvD@RO]
