OL,6,FThe report said: "We believe Leeds has
OL,7,Ftoo large a paediatric cardiac
OL,8,Fsurgical programme for it to be
OL,9,Fallowed to fail."
OL,11,FTrust bosses said a new surgeon would
OL,12,Fjoin the team in January and more
OL,13,Fspecialist nurses were being trained.
OL,15,FChief medical officer Magnus Harrison
OL,16,Fsaid: "We have a robust action plan in
OL,17,Fplace to deliver the rest of the
OL,18,Frecommendations, which we are
OL,19,Fcommitted to delivering."
