OL,6,FA separate review was carried out into
OL,7,Fthe care of seven children operated on
OL,8,Fby the same surgeon, including two who
OL,9,Fdied.
OL,11,FThe unnamed surgeon, who was placed on
OL,12,Frestricted duties, was found to have
OL,13,Fperformed well in three of the complex
OL,14,Fcases but there were concerns over a
OL,15,Ffurther four.
OL,17,FAn eighth case was still being
OL,18,Freviewed by Andrew Parry, a Bristol-
OL,19,Fbased paediatric cardiac surgeon.
