OL,6,FDr Harrison said the trust had offered
OL,7,Fto meet the children's families.
OL,9,FHe said: "I would like to thank the
OL,10,Fparents of those seven children whose
OL,11,Fcare we reviewed and extend my sincere
OL,12,Fcondolences to the families of the two
OL,13,Fchildren who sadly died.
OL,15,F"I am deeply sorry that in four
OL,16,Fchildren's cases, the findings
OL,17,Findicate that there were elements of
OL,18,Fcare that could have been improved.
